* ''[[Laticauda_frontalis|Laticauda frontalis]]'' <small>([[Charles_Walter_De_Vis|De Vis]], 1905)</small>
* ''[[Laticauda_guineai|Laticauda guineai]]'' <small>[[Harold_F._Heatwole|Heatwole]], [[Stephen_D._Busack|Busack]] & [[Harold_Cogger|Cogger]], 2005</small> – Guinea's sea krait
* [[扁尾海蛇|扁尾海蛇]] ''[[Laticauda_laticaudata|Laticauda laticaudata]]'' <small>([[Carl_Linnaeus|Linnaeus]], [[10th_edition_of_Systema_Naturae|1758]])</small>：又名[[黑唇青斑海蛇|黑唇青斑海蛇]]。
